{
  "texts": [
    "Accordingly, the following data were extracted from the full text articles:",
    "1) Demographic data (age, gender, ethnicity, sample size, and skeletal discrepancy).",
    "2) Characteristics of the study (study design, asymmetry criteria, and comparison groups).",
    "3) Features of MSP construction (3D technique, software used, MSP type, nomenclature used, construction technique, and reference points).",
    "4) Features of the analysis (landmark digitization, asymmetry assessment, reliability assessment, and measurement type)."
  ]
}